 It sounds like a sensible idea. 

00:00:25.220 --> 00:00:26.540
 The Basal 

00:00:26.620 --> 00:00:30.700
 Back doors have been allowed for old-fashioned phone calls for decades. 

00:00:30.880 --> 00:00:31.860
 They are called interceptions. 

