 It's called "wiretaps" in English, because the police many years ago 

00:00:43.620 --> 00:00:48.280
 Literally would put a device into a physical telephone line. 

00:00:48.280 --> 00:00:50.020
 So for anyone who grew up knowing this, 

00:00:50.020 --> 00:00:51.649
 anyone who has grown up with computers like this, 

